Sentencas: Systematic microstructural analyses have been carried out on a series of technological SOFCs that went through long-term cell tests with various operating parameters including temperature, current load and time length under current.
Titulo: Microstructure degradation of LSM-YSZ cathode in SOFCs operated at various conditions

Sentencas: For the LSM-YSZ cathode, a number of microstructure degradation mechanisms have been identified.
Titulo: Microstructure degradation of LSM-YSZ cathode in SOFCs operated at various conditions

Sentencas: And it has been observed that different mechanisms dominate the degradation process under different test conditions.
Titulo: Microstructure degradation of LSM-YSZ cathode in SOFCs operated at various conditions

Sentencas: The severe cathode degradation at 750 degrees C operation with high current density is attributed to a loss of the cathode/electrolyte interface stability.
Titulo: Microstructure degradation of LSM-YSZ cathode in SOFCs operated at various conditions

Sentencas: For the cells tested at 850 degrees C, the interface stability is maintained due to further sintering during cell operation.
Titulo: Microstructure degradation of LSM-YSZ cathode in SOFCs operated at various conditions

Sentencas: A cell test lasting for 2 years (17500 h) at 850 degrees C with a moderate current density (not greater than 1 A/cm(2)) has shown that the cathode microstructure is fairly robust to the degradation processes at this temperature, such as grain coarsening and element diffusion.
Titulo: Microstructure degradation of LSM-YSZ cathode in SOFCs operated at various conditions

Sentencas: The cell degrades mildly with a cell voltage degradation rate of 7 mV/1000 h. (C) 2011 Elsevier B.V.
Titulo: Microstructure degradation of LSM-YSZ cathode in SOFCs operated at various conditions
